<h2 style="color: #1e293b; font-size: 22px; font-weight: 700; margin-top: 0; margin-bottom: 12px; text-align: center; font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Segoe UI', Roboto, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;">Password Reset Request</h2>
<p style="color: #475569; font-size: 15px; line-height: 1.6; margin-bottom: 24px; text-align: center; font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Segoe UI', Roboto, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;">
  Hello <strong><%= userName %></strong>,<br>We received a request to reset your password. Please use the secure verification OTP code below to complete the process:
</p>

<div style="background: linear-gradient(135deg, #6366f1, #a855f7); padding: 24px; text-align: center; border-radius: 12px; margin: 24px 0; box-shadow: 0 10px 15px -3px rgba(99, 102, 241, 0.3);">
  <span style="font-size: 36px; font-weight: 800; letter-spacing: 8px; color: #ffffff; font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Segoe UI', Roboto, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;">
    <%= resetCode %>
  </span>
</div>

<p style="color: #64748b; font-size: 13px; text-align: center; margin-bottom: 0; line-height: 1.6; font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Segoe UI', Roboto, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;">
  This secure code will expire in <strong style="color: #1e293b;">10 minutes</strong>.<br>
  If you did not request a password change, you can safely ignore this email.
</p>
